FIG. 7 is a detail cross-sectional view illustrating a modification;


FIG. 8 is a detail cross-sectional view of a storm sewer manhole cover frame fitted with an internal plastic skirt;


FIG. 9 is a detail cross-sectional view of a sanitary sewer manhole cover frame fitted with an internal plastic skirt; and


FIG. 10 is a cross-sectional view of a manhole cover for a sanitary sewer.
